        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "(eighteen twelve to eighteen eighty two)",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Auerbach's biography is one of industry rather than of incident.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His birth was humble.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His life was long.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He wrote voluminously and was widely popular, to be half forgotten within a decade after his death.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Of Jewish parentage, his birthplace being Nordstetten, Wuertemberg (eighteen twelve), Auerbach drifted from preparation for the synagogue toward law, philosophy, and literature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The study of Spinoza (whose works he translated) gave form to his convictions concerning human life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "It led him to spend his literary talents on materials so various as the homely simplicity of peasant scenes and peasant souls, on the one hand, and on the other the popularization of a high social and ethical philosophy, specially inculcated through his larger fictions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His college education was obtained at Tuebingen, Munich, and Heidelberg.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Necessity rather than ambition prompted him to write, and he wrote as long as he lived.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "In eighteen forty three came the first set of the famous 'Schwarzwaelder Dorfgeschichten' (Black Forest Village Stories), followed by a second group in eighteen forty eight. These won instant and wide favor, and were widely translated.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His writings of this date-tales, sketches journalistic, political, and dramatic, and other papers-reveal Auerbach's varying moods or enthusiasms, chronicle his residence in different German or Austrian cities, and are comparatively insignificant among his forty or more volumes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Nor is much to be said of his first long fiction, 'Neues Leben' (New Life).",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His plan of making ethics the chief end of a novel was here exhibited at its best; he never again showed the same force of conception which got his imperfect literary art forgiven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The close of his life was much embittered by the growth of the anti-semitic sentiment; and his residence in Germany was merely nominal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "'On the Heights' is doubtless Auerbach's best representative.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "'The Villa on the Rhine' is in a lower key, with less appealing types, and less attractive local color.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Moreover, it is weighted with more philosophizing, and its movement is slower.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "In 'On the Heights' the emotional situations are strong.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "In spite of sentimentality, a true feeling animates its technique.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The atmosphere of a German royal residence, as he reveals it, appears almost as heavy as the real thing. Auerbach's humor is leaden; he finds it necessary to explain his own attempts at it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "But the peasant nurse Walpurga, her husband Hansei, and the aged grandmother in the family, are admirable delineations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "But in spite of all its defects it is a novel that should not be forgotten.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "For reflective readers it will always hold a charm, and its latent strength is proved by its triumph over its own faults.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "THE FIRST MASS",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "One Saturday afternoon the busy sound of hammer and adze was heard on the green hill top which served the good folks of Nordstetten as their open air gathering place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Valentine the carpenter, with his two sons, was making a scaffolding, designed to serve no less a purpose than that of an altar and a pulpit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Gregory, the son of Christian the tailor, was to officiate at his first mass and preach his first sermon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "With his bare head and feet he ran up and down the timbers as nimbly as a squirrel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "When a beam was being lifted, he cried, \"Pry under!\" as lustily as any one, put his shoulder to the crowbar, and puffed as if nine tenths of the weight fell upon him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Valentine liked to see his little boy employed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He would tell him to wind the twine on the reel, to carry the tools where they were wanted, or to rake the chips into a heap.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000015_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000015_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Once, when he perched upon the end of a plank for the purpose of weighing it down, the motion of the saw shook his every limb, and made him laugh aloud in spite of himself; he would have fallen off but for the eagerness with which he held on to his position and endeavored to perform his task in the most workmanlike manner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "At last the scaffolding was finished.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Lewis the saddler was ready to nail down the carpets and hanging.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "His father's whistle aroused him, and he ran to his side.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"Father,\" said Ivo, \"I wish I was in Hochdorf.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"Why?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"Because it's so near to heaven, and I should like to climb up once.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"You silly boy, it only seems as if heaven began there.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "From Hochdorf it is a long way to Stuttgart, and from there it is a long way to heaven yet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"How long?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "\"Well, you can't get there until you die.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Leading his little son with one hand, and carrying his tools in the other, Valentine passed through the village.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Washing and scouring was going on everywhere, and chairs and tables stood before the houses,--for every family expected visitors for the great occasion of the morrow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "As Valentine passed Christian the tailor's, he held his hand to his cap, prepared to take it off if anybody should look out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "But nobody did so: the place was silent as a cloister.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000024_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000024_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Some farmers' wives were going in, carrying bowls covered with their aprons, while others passed out with empty bowls under their arms.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "They nodded to each other without speaking: they had brought wedding presents for the young clergyman, who was to be married to his bride-the Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Next morning a clear, bright day rose upon the village.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He was to carry the crucifix.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Gretchen, Ivo's eldest sister, took him by the hand and led him into the street, \"so as to have room in the house.\" Having enjoined upon him by no means to go back, she returned hastily.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Wherever he came he found the men standing in knots in the road.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "They were but half dressed for the festival, having no coats on, but displaying their dazzling white shirt sleeves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Here and there women or girls were to be seen running from house to house without bodices, and with their hair half untied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He would have been delighted to have appeared like the grown folks,--first in negligee, and then in full dress amid the tolling of bells and the clang of trumpets; but he did not dare to return, or even to sit down anywhere, for fear of spoiling his clothes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He went through the village almost on tiptoe.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Wagon after wagon rumbled in, bringing farmers and farmers' wives from abroad; at the houses people welcomed them, and brought chairs to assist them in getting down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "All the world looked as exultingly quiet and glad as a community preparing to receive a hero who had gone forth from their midst and was returning after a victory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "From the church to the hill top the road was strewn with flowers and grass, which sent forth aromatic odors.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000026_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000026_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The squire was seen coming out of Christian the tailor's, and only covered his head when he found himself in the middle of the street.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The squire's wife soon followed, leading her daughter Barbara, who was but six years old, by the hand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Barbara was dressed in bridal array.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "She wore the veil and the wreath upon her head, and a beautiful gown.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "As an immaculate virgin, she was intended to represent the bride of the young clergyman, the Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "At the first sound of the bell the people in shirt sleeves disappeared as if by magic.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Amid the ringing of all the bells, the procession at last issued from the church door.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The pennons waved, the band of music brought from Horb struck up, and the audible prayers of the men and women mingled with the sound.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000029_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000029_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The squire's Barbara, who carried a burning taper wreathed with rosemary, had gone before him and took her stand at the side of the altar.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000029_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000029_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The mass began; and at the tinkling of the bell all fell upon their faces, and not a sound would have been heard, had not a flight of pigeons passed directly over the altar with that fluttering and chirping noise which always accompanies their motion through the air.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "The chaplain of Horb now entered the pulpit, and solemnly addressed the \"permitiant.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "Then the latter took his place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "He understood little of the sermon; but his eyes hung upon the preacher's lips, and his mind followed his intentions if not his thoughts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5565_40589_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5565/40589/5565_40589_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5565",
        "content": "As the crowd dispersed, every one spoke in raptures of the \"gentleman\" and of the happiness of the parents of such a son.",
